data.description: REDUCED PRICE & 2.5% INTEREST! Qualify to assume the current loan on this beautiful home w/ spacious rooms throughout! Spacious front entry welcomes you to dining or living spaces. 2 gas fireplaces. 2 sizable main floor bdrms w/ wood floors. Eat-in galley kitchen w/ new flooring & countertops! Main level laundry & 3/4 bath. Bsmt family room and bonus space. Most of the interior of home is being or has been painted. Private backyard w/ storage shed included. BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT OF HOME!
